Welcome to mysterious world of witches and wizards! This game features five reels, nine paylines and accepts up to five coins. The Mummy is a Scatter symbol, at least three Scatters anywhere on the reels activate Free Spins feature! The Werewolf symbol is wild and substitutes for any other symbol (except Bonus and Scatter) to complete a winning combination. Besides, a combination of at least three Vampires starts "The Shady Conquest" bonus game! Symbols in Mystic Slots pay left-to-right and right-to-left!